1. *Rešiti* ćemo sve probleme koji su nastali (We will solve all the problems that have arisen).

2. Moramo da *rešimo* svoje lične probleme (We need to solve our personal problems).

3. Ona je rešila da ode odatle (She decided to leave from there).

4. *Rešivaću* tu situaciju sama (I will solve this situation by myself).

5. Oni su *rešili* da se presele u drugu državu (They decided to move to another country).

6. Nastojali smo da *rešimo* ovaj problem do sada (We have been trying to solve this problem so far).